data.description: Amazing opportunity - 3 bed/2 bath 4-sided brick ranch on 2 acres! Gorgeous pond view with water frontage! Fabulous bones on an incredible parcel; priced to allow buyers to make cosmetic updates. Main level offers family room, dining room, kitchen with 6'x6' walk-in pantry, primary with en-suite bath, and 2 additional bedrooms/full bath. Build instant equity and double the sq footage by finishing the 1,326 sq ft lower level, boasting kitchenette, full bath and laundry room. Covered front porch, covered rear patio and attached 2-car garage. Gorgeous 2-acre lot offers the best that country living has to offer! Don't let this rare opportunity pass you by!!!
